   <body>
      <prereq>
         <ul>
            <li>You can delete a file only if you have attached it.</li>
         </ul>
      </prereq>
      <context>You can delete files that are attached to forms.</context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>To access the appropriate file to be deleted, perform the following steps:</p>
            <p>
               <ol>
                  <li>In the navigation pane, click the appropriate form.<p>The form list page is displayed.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>In the tool bar, click <uicontrol>More</uicontrol>, and then click<uicontrol>Attachments</uicontrol>.<p>The attachments of all the forms are listed.</p>
                     <p>Various document management features are available for attachments. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content">For information on document management features, refer to <xref href="../../Document_Management/Doc_Mgmt.xml">Document Management</xref>.</ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To delete an attachment, select the appropriate file, and then click <image href="../../Icons/AttDel.png" placement="inline">
                  <alt>Delete</alt>
               </image>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
